      "id": "res_8aef1be6-9d72-44b9-b7cf-5db2645f00c3",
      "name": "DupeCore",
      "slug": "dupecore",
      "shortDescription": "A all in one dupe skript! Item blacklisting, and lifesteal!",
      "description": "DupeCore & Lifesteal Skript – Ultimate Duplication & PvP System\n\n\nTake your server to the next level with DupeCore, the all-in-one Duplication and Lifesteal system! This Skript is designed for serious Minecraft servers looking to add advanced item duplication mechanics without breaking the game balance, alongside a toggleable PvP lifesteal system for competitive gameplay.\n\n\nFeatures:\n\n\nSafe Duplication System: Duplicate any item in your hand with /dupe [amount]. Fully compatible with all standard Minecraft items and shulker boxes. Blacklist support prevents overpowered or rare items from being duplicated.\nShulker Box Safety: Any shulker box, regardless of color, is checked for blacklisted items to stop hidden exploits.\nCooldown Management: Prevents spamming with fully configurable cooldowns via /dupecooldown.\nLifesteal PvP: Toggle lifesteal on or off with {@lifesteal-enabled}. Kill another player to gain hearts and subtract them from your target, with a max of 20 hearts.\nHeart Economy: Players can withdraw hearts as red dye items with /withdraw and redeem them by right-clicking. Hearts cannot be duplicated or abused.\nAdmin Tools: /dupeblacklist to manage restricted items\n\nWhy choose DupeCore?\nThis Skript is professional, secure, and ready for monetization. Perfect for servers that want a fun but balanced duplication system combined with engaging PvP mechanics. Safe, easy to use, and fully configurable.",
